
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>O Último Guardião da Floresta</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#06110a;
      --panel:#0d1a12ee;
      --panel-2:#13251a;
      --line:#3f7d49;
      --gold:#e7c35a;
      --life:#5cff8b;
      --danger:#ff6b6b;
      --text:#eef8ee;
      --muted:#b9ccb8;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      --pixel: "Courier New", monospace;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{margin:0;height:100%;background:#000;overflow:hidden;font-family:var(--pixel)}
    body{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}

    .game-shell{
      position:relative;
      width:min(100vw, 1280px);
      height:min(100vh, 720px);
      background:#000;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    }

    canvas{
      display:block;
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
      image-rendering: pixelated;
      image-rendering: crisp-edges;
      background:#06110a;
    }

    .screen{
      position:absolute; inset:0;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      z-index:20;
    }

    /* Tela inicial usando a imagem de arte fornecida pelo usuário */
    #menuScreen{
      background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      background-repeat:no-repeat;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    #menuScreen::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute; inset:0;
      background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,.55) 100%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .forest-silhouette,.forest-silhouette::before,.forest-silhouette::after{
      position:absolute; inset:auto 0 0 0; content:"";
      display:block;
      height:55%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 8% 35%, rgba(8,27,12,.95) 0 10%, transparent 11%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 30%, rgba(8,27,12,.95) 0 11%, transparent 12%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 31% 28%, rgba(8,27,12,.98) 0 14%, transparent 15%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 49% 24%, rgba(8,27,12,.98) 0 13%, transparent 14%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 67% 30%, rgba(8,27,12,.98) 0 14%, transparent 15%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 79% 26%, rgba(8,27,12,.95) 0 11%, transparent 12%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 35%, rgba(8,27,12,.95) 0 10%, transparent 11%),
        linear-gradient(to top, #031007 0%, #05150b 60%, transparent 100%);
      opacity:.95;
    }
    .forest-silhouette::before{height:78%; opacity:.7; filter:blur(1px); transform:scale(1.05)}
    .forest-silhouette::after{height:95%; opacity:.45; filter:blur(2px); transform:scale(1.1)}

    .menu-inner{
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      padding:28px 24px 36px;
    }

    .title-wrap{
      margin-top:8px;
      text-align:center;
      color:#e9e1c2;
      text-shadow:
        0 2px 0 #40361c,
        0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.75);
      letter-spacing:2px;
    }

    .title-top{
      font-size:clamp(34px,6vw,86px);
      font-weight:900;
      line-height:.92;
      color:#7fd85f;
      filter:drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(117,255,96,.2));
    }
    .title-bottom{
      font-size:clamp(44px,7vw,110px);
      font-weight:900;
      line-height:.95;
      margin-top:2px;
      color:#d7cfaf;
    }
    .subtitle{
      margin-top:10px;
      font-size:clamp(12px,1.3vw,24px);
      color:#e9ddb0;
    }

    .hero-figure{
      position:relative;
      width:min(42vw, 360px);
      height:min(46vh, 360px);
      margin-top:auto;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .hero-figure .cloak{
      position:absolute; left:50%; top:18%;
      width:55%; height:65%;
      transform:translateX(-50%);
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg,#17331f,#27492e 35%,#0a150d 100%);
      clip-path:polygon(40% 0, 64% 6%, 76% 28%, 92% 100%, 10% 100%, 24% 30%);
      filter:drop-shadow(0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.45));
    }
    .hero-figure .body{
      position:absolute; left:50%; top:26%;
      width:26%; height:36%;
      transform:translateX(-50%);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2e4f2e,#1a271b 70%,#120f09);
      border:3px solid rgba(0,0,0,.2);
    }
    .hero-figure .head{
      position:absolute; left:50%; top:12%;
      width:20%; height:18%;
      transform:translateX(-50%);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 35% 38%, #2b1d12 0 18%, #0000 19%),
        linear-gradient(180deg,#1d140f,#6f552b 55%,#2e2012 100%);
      filter:brightness(.85);
    }
    .hero-figure .arm{
      position:absolute; left:58%; top:34%;
      width:26%; height:10%;
      transform:rotate(-16deg);
      transform-origin:left center;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,#2d2f1c,#87703b);
    }
    .hero-figure .magic{
      position:absolute; left:76%; top:22%;
      width:22%; aspect-ratio:1;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle, rgba(144,255,100,.95) 0 18%, rgba(144,255,100,.4) 22%, rgba(80,255,140,.18) 44%, transparent 66%);
      filter:blur(1px) drop-shadow(0 0 18px rgba(126,255,110,.8));
      animation: pulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-figure .magic::before,
    .hero-figure .magic::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute; inset:18%;
      border:2px solid rgba(167,255,145,.5);
      border-radius:50%;
      animation: ripple 2s linear infinite;
    }
    .hero-figure .magic::after{animation-delay:1s}

    .waterfall{
      position:absolute; left:22%; bottom:20%;
      width:6%; height:26%;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(180,220,255,.85), rgba(180,220,255,.18));
      filter:blur(1px);
      opacity:.9;
    }

    .play-btn{
      position:absolute;
      left:50%;
      bottom:8%;
      transform:translateX(-50%);
      z-index:5;
      width:auto;
      min-width:220px;
      height:auto;
      min-height:60px;
      padding:14px 48px;
      border:3px solid var(--gold);
      border-radius:6px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,40,24,.85), rgba(8,20,12,.9));
      color:var(--gold);
      font-family:var(--pixel);
      font-size:clamp(18px,2.6vw,28px);
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:3px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.5), 0 0 18px rgba(231,195,90,.25) inset;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:transform .15s ease, filter .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
    }
    .play-btn::before{
      content:"▶ JOGAR";
    }
    .play-btn:hover{filter:brightness(1.25); box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.5), 0 0 26px rgba(231,195,90,.55) inset; transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1.04)}
    .play-btn:active{transform:translateX(-50%) scale(.96)}

    .hud{
      position:absolute;
      inset:16px 16px auto 16px;
      z-index:10;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .hud-group{
      display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;
      pointer-events:auto;
    }

    .hud-pill{
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
      background:var(--panel);
      border:2px solid rgba(108,168,102,.45);
      color:var(--text);
      padding:8px 12px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
      min-height:44px;
    }

    .life-box{
      width:min(38vw, 280px);
      display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:5px;
      background:var(--panel);
      border:2px solid rgba(108,168,102,.45);
      padding:8px 10px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .life-bar{
      width:100%; height:14px; background:#1c2a1f; border:2px solid #48664e; overflow:hidden;
    }
    .life-fill{
      height:100%;
      width:100%;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,#4ef08d,#b6ff7a);
      transition:width .2s ease;
      box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(103,255,144,.35) inset;
    }

    .icon{
      font-size:16px;
      width:20px;text-align:center;
      filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.4));
    }

    .pause-btn{
      pointer-events:auto;
      border:none;
      background:var(--panel);
      color:var(--text);
      border:2px solid rgba(108,168,102,.45);
      padding:10px 14px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font:inherit;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      transition:transform .15s ease, background .2s ease;
    }
    .pause-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px); background:#14271a}
    .pause-btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}

    .overlay{
      position:absolute; inset:0;
      display:none;
      align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      z-index:30;
      background:rgba(2,9,6,.62);
      backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
      padding:20px;
    }
    .overlay.show{display:flex}

    .panel{
      width:min(92vw, 520px);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,26,18,.96), rgba(9,17,12,.96));
      border:2px solid rgba(130,190,120,.45);
      box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
      color:var(--text);
      padding:28px;
      text-align:center;
    }
    .panel h2{
      margin:0 0 10px;
      font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px);
      letter-spacing:2px;
    }
    .panel p{color:var(--muted); margin:8px 0 20px; line-height:1.5}
    .actions{display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn{
      border:none;
      padding:12px 18px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font:inherit;
      color:#f4ffe8;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2b5730,#18371d);
      border:2px solid #6aa46f;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      transition:transform .15s ease, filter .2s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px); filter:brightness(1.08)}
    .btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
    .btn.alt{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#4d3920,#2d1f0f); border-color:#b7924f}

    .hint{
      position:absolute;
      left:16px; bottom:16px;
      z-index:11;
      background:rgba(9,18,12,.76);
      color:#d7e6d5;
      border:1px solid rgba(130,190,120,.25);
      padding:8px 10px;
      font-size:12px;
      backdrop-filter:blur(4px);
    }

    .hidden{display:none !important}

    @keyframes pulse{
      0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}
      50%{transform:scale(1.08)}
    }
    @keyframes ripple{
      from{transform:scale(.6); opacity:.8}
      to{transform:scale(1.4); opacity:0}
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .hud{inset:10px 10px auto 10px; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start}
      .life-box{width:min(86vw, 360px)}
      .title-top{font-size:clamp(32px,10vw,62px)}
      .title-bottom{font-size:clamp(42px,12vw,74px)}
      .hero-figure{width:54vw;height:32vh}
      .play-btn{min-width:78vw}
      .hint{font-size:11px; right:10px; left:10px}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="game-shell">
    <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="1280" height="720" aria-label="Jogo O Último Guardião da Floresta"></canvas>

    <section id="menuScreen" class="screen" aria-label="Tela inicial">
      <div class="menu-inner" style="position:relative;padding:0;">
        <button id="playBtn" class="play-btn" aria-label="Jogar"></button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div id="hud" class="hud hidden">
      <div class="hud-group">
        <div class="life-box">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;font-size:12px">
            <span>VIDA</span>
            <span id="lifeText">100 / 100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="life-bar"><div id="lifeFill" class="life-fill"></div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="hud-pill"><span class="icon">✦</span><span id="scoreText">0</span></div>
        <div class="hud-pill"><span class="icon">🪙</span><span id="coinText">0</span></div>
        <div class="hud-pill"><span class="icon">⛶</span><span id="phaseText">Fase 1</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="hud-group">
        <button id="pauseBtn" class="pause-btn" aria-label="Pausar jogo">⏸ Pausar</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="pauseOverlay" class="overlay">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>JOGO PAUSADO</h2>
        <p>Respire fundo. A floresta ainda precisa de você.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn" id="resumeBtn">Continuar</button>
          <button class="btn alt" id="restartBtn">Reiniciar</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="gameOverOverlay" class="overlay">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>GAME OVER</h2>
        <p>O guardião caiu, mas a floresta ainda pode ser salva em outra tentativa.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn" id="retryBtn">Tentar novamente</button>
          <button class="btn alt" id="backMenuBtn1">Voltar ao menu</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="victoryOverlay" class="overlay">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>VITÓRIA</h2>
        <p>Você derrotou a ameaça da floresta sombria e restaurou o equilíbrio.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <button class="btn" id="playAgainBtn">Jogar novamente</button>
          <button class="btn alt" id="backMenuBtn2">Voltar ao menu</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="transitionOverlay" class="overlay">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>TRANSIÇÃO DE FASE</h2>
        <p id="transitionText">Avançando...</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hint" id="hintBox">
      Controles: ← → ou A D para mover • Espaço para pular • 1 para atacar • Esc para pausar
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    (() => {
      "use strict";

      const canvas = document.getElementById("gameCanvas");
      const ctx = canvas.getContext("2d");

      const ui = {
        menu: document.getElementById("menuScreen"),
        hud: document.getElementById("hud"),
